i/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢又無咩點叫"},{"pid":"6b041dd4a3caea6ddcc39d3f34cf8369242973cb","tid":154064,"uid":84658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"我都好擔心主人絕左育之後會冇咁活躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df230834cfd92b1e4757adca3abf9fd244b86e8","tid":154064,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好擔心主人絕左育之後會冇咁活躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家我主人都會跑黎跑去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好怕之後好懶"},{"pid":"990f5cbd10f617e4744f4b51fad2b5c365d07275","tid":154064,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"唔一定要絕育既<br />\n不過佢發情時會叫足一星期特別係夜晚<br />\n你頂得順就得，一段2歲半後就會叫春<br />\n如要絕育價錢大概800-1200左右<br />\n幾年前就係800有得做但我想養喵保留返佢既天性"},{"pid":"4a9575aaab1d9a7248a609b0f88dd82c7e58b587","tid":154064,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔一定要絕育既<br />\n不過佢發情時會叫足一星期特別係夜晚<br />\n你頂得順就得，一段2歲半後就會叫春<br />\n如要絕育價錢大概800-1200左右<br />\n幾年前就係800有得做但我想養喵保留返佢既天性</blockquote><br />\n所以你家主人無絕到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac7cda7669a7b75bd3f7d73ade719f68569a40c","tid":154064,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"男仔唔絕育會週圍噴尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1e48214acd27cbc26e186f48a5a522b9d12906","tid":154064,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男仔唔絕育會週圍噴尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕左都會<br />\n<br />\n我果隻6個月就絕左，最好早啲做<br />\n同埋做完佢會乖啲。好多時啲狗走失就係因為發情"},{"pid":"12cb950055965c5baecbb4781aae8b79e724b6d9","tid":154064,"uid":70877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好擔心主人絕左育之後會冇咁活躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都有擔心過 <br />\n但屋企個兩隻絕完育玩得仲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲超級嗲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c107e5a5653e55b1690673bcae869398b6ad605","tid":154064,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男仔唔絕育會週圍噴尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕左都會<br />\n<br />\n我果隻6個月就絕左，最好早啲做<br />\n同埋做完佢會乖啲。好多時啲狗走失就係因為發情</blockquote><br />\n點樣乖法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我個人認為我主人而家已經好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d36915965f1dfaefbd48146c60b784f514e08c","tid":154064,"uid":64354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"我主人係港九做絕育 手勢唔錯價錢都可以<br />\n埋單好似980$"}]}